metadata.name: FullEX/FullHD
metadata.description:
The work from "Between Kyiv and Berlin" collection.

The work is talking about value of real experience nowadays. In a time that everything can be brought to you thought the screen, real emotions are only possible with full experience. Which is much better than full HD)

Location: Warsaw
Model: Tess Orlova (@o7l0v)
1545 × 1024 pixels, Jpeg
